Wilfred Shine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilfred_Shine 0 Wilfred Shine (12 July 1864 – 14 March 1939 in Kingston-Upon-Thames, England) was a British actor, mainly on the stage, and a specialist in melodrama.
